{"html": [{"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">EXTRACTO DE RESOLUCION N&#xBA; 1.505 EXENTA, DE 2007 </div></div>", "i": 7353084}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Por resoluci&#xF3;n exenta N&#xBA; 1.505, de 17 de agosto de 2007, se revoc&#xF3; la autorizaci&#xF3;n otorgada en conformidad a lo dispuesto en el N&#xBA; 5 de la resoluci&#xF3;n N&#xBA; 65, de 2000, del Ministerio de Transportes y Telecomunicaciones, a los talleres que a continuaci&#xF3;n se individualizan:</div><br><div class=\"p\">Empresa&nbsp; &nbsp;  Nombre del&nbsp; Direcci&#xF3;n del&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  Ciudad</div><div class=\"p\">Habilitada&nbsp; Taller&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Taller</div><br><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; SHT&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  Polpaico Pje. N&#xBA; 2&nbsp; Puerto Montt</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Lote 22-23</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Sur Trade</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Ltda.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  Cardonal N&#xBA; 1963&nbsp; &nbsp; Puerto Montt</div><div class=\"p\">Abastible</div><div class=\"p\">S.A.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Servicio</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; T&#xE9;cnico&nbsp; &nbsp;  Ej&#xE9;rcito N&#xBA; 553&nbsp; &nbsp;  Osorno</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Autosorno</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Ltda.</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Imtefar</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Ltda.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  Av. Bulnes N&#xBA; 875&nbsp;  Temuco</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Piamonte</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; S.A.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Agustinas N&#xBA; 2138&nbsp;  Santiago</div><br></div>", "i": 7353085}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Dan